--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project structure:

src/main/java:
	com.config:
		Config.properties
		
	com.pages:
	    Page01_LandingPage.java
	    Page02_ProductListPage.java
	    Page03_ProductDetailsPage.java
		
			
	com.utility:
		Config.java
		ConfigReader.java
		Utility.java
		
src/test/java:
	com.apphooks:
		ApplicationHooks.java
	
	productdetails_stepdefinition_1
		ProductDetails_StepDefinition_1.java
		
	productdetails_stepdefinition_2
	    ProductDetails_StepDefinition_2.java
	    
	testrunner
		ProductDetails_TestRunner_1.java
		ProductDetails_TestRunner_2.java
		
src/main/resources:
	ReadMe
						
src/test/resources:
	features
		ProductDetails1.feature
		ProductDetails2.feature	

drivers folder:
	chromedriver.exe
	
screenshots folder:
	file.png	
	
pom.xml			
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project creation sequence:

Create maven project
Add the dependencies in pom.xml
Maven project will have 4 sections by default(if not then create them):
	src/main/java
	src/main/resources
	src/test/java
	src/test/resources

Create the required packages, classes, files in them as per below sequence:

Step 1 --> Create Feature file
Step 2 --> Create Config.java
Step 3 --> Create Config.properties
Step 4 --> Create ConfigReader.java
Step 5 --> Create Utility.java
Step 6 --> Create Page01_LandingPage.java
Step 7 --> Create Page02_ProductListPage.java
Step 8 --> Create Page03_ProductDetailsPage.java
Step 9 --> Create ApplicationHooks.java
Step 10 --> Create ProductDetails_StepDefinition_1.java
Step 11 --> Create ProductDetails_StepDefinition_2.java
Step 12 --> Create ProductDetails_TestRunner_1.java.java
Step 13 --> Create LoginPage_TestRunner.java
Step 14 --> Create ProductDetails_TestRunner_2.java.java

Create the drivers folder and keep driver in it
Create the screenshots folder to keep screenshots in it
Run the tests by using Test class(individual test class) or pom.xml or testng.xml

See the reports in test-output folder(created by testng)
See the reports in target folder(created by maven)
